{"tid":604258,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"三上悠亞組隊攻韓 逾4萬多韓仔請願要求撤出K-Pop界","createTime":"2018-03-24T13:53:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T14:45:54.000Z","uid":1886,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b0ecb06867bf9e20c7a8b66c663be0e22b88bd23","tid":604258,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T13:53:24.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180324/large/1521869239_e94a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180324%2Flarge%2F1521869239_e94a.jpg&h=53bd17cc&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n24歲日本AV界小天后三上悠亞進軍K-Pop界，並組成三人女子組合Honey Popcorn在韓國正式出道，但自從三上悠亞宣佈攻韓後卻引起不少爭議，更有當地歌迷嫌棄其AV女形象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，聲討三人撤出K-Pop界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180324/large/1521869238_428c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180324%2Flarge%2F1521869238_428c.jpg&h=6beac333&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\nHoney Popcorn由三位原本是偶像嘅AV女優組成，除主將三上悠亞外，仲有櫻萌子同松田美子，三人出道歌《Bibidi Babidi Boo》MV已告曝光。Honey Popcorn周三在韓國出道，可惜反應兩極，三上悠亞在記者會上表示：「我知道有人會覺得很難為我們應援。」三人出道的確引發韓國網友反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，有民眾因擔心三女教壞年輕人，上青瓦台嘅官網聯署「反對AV女優的韓國偶像團體出道」，截至昨晚已超過4萬2千人次參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180324/57989067\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180324%2F57989067&d=ZU2mIAMeqG50Epqbz%2BTAazM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=9e478c88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180324%2F57989067&h=3df4f68e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180324/57989067</a>"},{"pid":"9fcdaaecda84e2d86285d6aa0eed9a4aa58e8306","tid":604258,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T13:54:06.000Z","msg":"連署發起人認為韓國偶像對於粉絲擁有極大影響力，曾有離家出走粉絲聽了《Comeback Home》決定回家，仲有粉絲因為偶像拒收生日禮物決定集資幫偶像展開愛心捐款。請願概要中，更提及「Honey Popcorn成員的另一身份是在韓國被嚴格禁止的職業，禁止AV女優的國家卻讓AV女優以偶像身份出道，不太合理！」另外，韓國電視台一直以來也都嚴格審核偶像歌手嘅歌曲內容及演出，過度煽情或低水準都有可能被禁，發起人強調：「這都是因為偶像會帶給粉絲莫大的影響所訂下的規則。」《Bibidi Babidi Boo》話題性十足，MV在YouTube曝光後已破100萬人次觀看，但恐怕難有機會上節目表演及宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180324/large/1521869241_d85c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180324%2Flarge%2F1521869241_d85c.jpg&h=1761c9a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LAOT6JscCVU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLAOT6JscCVU&d=ZU2mIAMeqG50Epqbz%2BTAazM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=9e05482d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LAOT6JscCVU</a></div>"},{"pid":"e68a2863f65e76e9e343dca2adb72afe2d498669","tid":604258,"uid":171594,"like":8,"dislike":7,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T14:22:53.000Z","msg":"大把kpop女團私生活仲亂過av女優<br />\n只係冇俾人見到咁解<br />\n<br />\n冇人做av女優，你班人邊有得睇<br />\n我就唔信個班泡菜仔全部冇j過佢"},{"pid":"a155b53e95e0ce75abd37ebdf50c1cb1661aa8e1","tid":604258,"uid":78392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T14:32:27.000Z","msg":"又要j又要屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f5a5fc100f850765932a81c8601d8e105920b6","tid":604258,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T14:35:54.000Z","msg":"睇開你唔著杉<br />\n而家有杉就算幾少都係多'<br />\n定係韓仔支持本土AV<br />\n韓妹啲三級片好撚柒正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83be157b751ada35b21f7b66b098c4138737a69b","tid":604258,"uid":108386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T14:45:54.000Z","msg":"月巴"}]}